	<p>Sam Grigg Design bridges the gap between concept and reality; between vapor ware and development. If your job is to think up ways to improve your business, my job is to understand your ideas and drag them (kicking and screaming) out into the light of day. If the devil is in the details, then I am the devil. The implementation of your product is likely to be more complex than you realize. The balm that relieves the irritation of half-baked ideas comes in a gray box. I have the skills and experience to pull your ideas out of the moist, dark, damp corners of your brain and bring them to life.</p>
	<p>Putting the look and feel on your idea is always going to be tricky. You may have designers on staff. You may know a guy.  You may not even know what I mean when I say "look and feel". I can help in each scenario. I'm happy to work with your designers or to do the design myself.</p>
	<p>When it comes to development, you may have in-house development, you may outsource it, or you may have nothing. In all three scenarios I can help. I can either work with your development team, with your contractors, or I can introduce you to some contractors. In (nearly) any scenario, we can make it work.</p>
